item.title: Imperial College Model United Nations takes on LIMUN
item.author: Hana Dowidar,
item.description: Imperial College Model United Nations sent twelve of its finest delegates (and two chairs!) off to Europe’s biggest MUN conference, LIMUN. We showed up bright-eyed and eager on Friday afternoon, ready for what we knew would doubtlessly be a great weekend. And boy were we right! It was a weekend …
